'''迈克尔·M·戈特斯曼'''（{{lang-en|Michael M. Gottesman}}，{{bd|1946年|10月7日|}}）是一位美国[[生物化学|生物化学]]家<ref name="cbmm">[http://orwh.od.nih.gov/pharmacology/speak.html Biography] {{Wayback|url=http://orwh.od.nih.gov/pharmacology/speak.html |date=20100527173333 }} as a speaker at the 1999 Conference on Biologic and Molecular Mechanisms for Sex Differences in Pharmacokinetics, Pharmacodynamics, and Pharmacogenetics, Office of Research on Women's Health, retrieved 2010-02-28.</ref>，曾任美国[[國家衛生院_(美國)|國家衛生院]]副院长及下属的[[国家癌症研究所|国家癌症研究所]]细胞生物学实验室主任<ref>[http://ccr.nci.nih.gov/staff/staff.asp?profileid=5713 Staff profile] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100527100910/http://ccr.nci.nih.gov/staff/staff.asp?profileid=5713 |date=2010-05-27 }}, NCI, retrieved 2010-02-28.</ref>。

